=head2 test_freeze -- test a simple relaxation case

=for ref

This routine relaxes an extremely simple fluxon system to exercise the
relaxer and force laws.

This file is part of FLUX 2.0, released 31-Oct-2007.

=cut

use strict;
use warnings;
use PDL;
use Flux;
$a = read_world('menagerie/simple-8.flux');
$a->verbosity(1);
$a->b_flag(0);
$a->forces('f_pressure_equi','f_curvature','f_vertex');
simple_relaxer($a,0,0,200);
$a->fix_proximity(1);
$a->fix_curvature(0.25);
simple_relaxer($a,0,0,500);